title: 1973 1974 1975 1976 1977 1978 Pontiac Firebird Trans Am Sail Panel Bird Decals - Orange
description: This is an exact reproduction, GM Restoration Parts decal kit for a 1973, 1974, 1975, 1976, 1977, 1978 Firebird/Formula/Trans Am . This user-complete kit equips you with everything necessary to restore your vehicle to its original appearance. This is not like other kits on Amazon. It is correct, licensed and accepted as the industry standard for concourse restorations. Phoenix Graphix is proud to officially announce its presentation of the 1973 1974 1975 1976 1977 1978 Pontiac Firebird Trans Am Sail Panel Bird Decals. General Motors introduced the iconic Firebird hood decal on Trans Am in 1973. It was an immediate success and the artwork lasted a full six model years. This art is now available to adorn any Pontiac Trans Am, Formula or Firebird. These smaller sail panel birds are produced to exact GM specifications (as used on Black Special Editions from 1976 thru 1978). We have them in all the original colors and they are screen printed with a high luster to compliment any vehicle or even your walls. This Firebird icon is one of the most recognized in automotive history and we have them for you to purchase!
